We are having lots of problems with our swerve drive, and we would like some example code that we can use to prove that our issues are not mechanical.

We are using:

SDS MK4i L2 with NEOs x 4
SparkMax controllers
CANCoder x 4
Pidgeon 2.0

Any code that is confirmed to work would be very useful to us!
